el</td><td width='499' align='left' bgcolor='#000000' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma'size='2'>4 - 6</td></tr><tr><td width='98' align='left' bgcolor='#21456B' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma' size='2'>Location</td><td width='499' align='left' bgcolor='#21456B' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma'size='2'>-2300, +1000</td></tr><tr><td width='98' align='left' bgcolor='#000000' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma' size='2'>Factions</td><td width='499' align='left' bgcolor='#000000' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma'size='2'>-Bristlebane</td></tr><tr><td width='98' align='left' bgcolor='#21456B' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma' size='2'>Spells Used</td><td width='499' align='left' bgcolor='#21456B' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma'size='2'>Fear, Clinging Darkness, Poison Bolt, Lifespike</td></tr><tr><td width='98' align='left' bgcolor='#000000' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma' size='2'>Strategy</td><td width='499' align='left' bgcolor='#000000' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma'size='2'>There are three bandits at the camp, and were indifferent to my gnome before I camped them.  This camp is very hard to break for a less than 8 gnome necromancer, so I recommend either getting a partner or someone to break it for you.

 

If you have to break it on your own, be prepared: it is tough.  Fear the lowest con, as fear is most likely to work on them.  The next two will rush you, and try to get off Poison Bolt on one.  Melee that one while casting Lifespike.  That bandit should die just as Fear breaks.  Kill the second one you pulled, which will cause you to go out of mana.  Now you have to melee this bandit, as your pet is usually dead.<br><br> 

If its already broken, hit the bandit with Clinging Darkness.  Then Poison Bolt her and melee for the rest of the battle.  Add a Lifespike to finish her off and regain some HP.<br><br>

Since the spawn time is only 5 minutes per Bandit, you will have just enough time to get to full mana.  This consta-camping is awesome experience.  Loot generally includes rusty weapons, up to 5gp, and the occasional food/container.<br><br></td></tr><tr><td width='98' align='left' bgcolor='#21456B' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma' size='2'>Author</td><td width='499' align='left' bgcolor='#21456B' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma'size='2'><a href ='mailto:'>Ektar Plasmar</td></tr><tr></table><br><br></table></div>